Buda kunze!

0:00:12.400,0:00:15.080
Ini ndinoti, "Buda!"

0:00:15.080,0:00:23.520
Iwe, mweya wakaipa - siya vanhu vangu!

0:00:23.520,0:00:29.460
Siya vanhu vangu!

0:00:29.460,0:00:40.540
Iye akabatwa nemweya wekukwezva varume uye mweya uyu wagara uri mumhuri yake.

0:00:40.540,0:00:42.080
Uchadzingirwa kunze.

0:00:42.080,0:00:43.700
Anoita sembwa.

0:00:43.700,0:00:47.960
Imbwa zvinoreva kuti, iye ari kungoita zvepabonde nemurume chero upi zvake.

0:00:47.960,0:00:51.960
Chero nguva iyo mweya unouya paari, iye anobva aita sechifeve.

0:00:51.960,0:00:56.600
Haasi kuenda kuhotera asi iye ari kurara pese pese.

0:00:56.600,0:01:00.940
Ndiro dambudziko raanaro.

0:01:00.940,0:01:02.880
Jesu anomuda.

0:01:02.880,0:01:04.340
Zvamataura ndezve chokwadi.

0:01:04.340,0:01:06.380
Ndakasvika pano nokuda kwekutsvaga rusununguko.

0:01:06.380,0:01:10.920
Ndange ndichinyengetera kuna Mwari nguva zhinji kuti andisunungure.

0:01:10.920,0:01:17.620
Mushure me svondo, mukadzi uyo akanga agamuchira huporofita akaonana na T.B. Joshua kuti adzikinurwe.

0:01:17.620,0:01:23.600
Pano, munhu wa Mwari anoshumira munyengetero nedzikinuro, nekumubata, muzita ra Jesu Kristu,

0:01:23.600,0:01:28.560
achitsigirwa, nekuperekedzwa nemasimba ose ekudenga.

0:01:28.560,0:01:32.620
Kununurwa kwake kunoitika uye iye asununguka.

0:01:32.620,0:01:36.940
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:01:36.940,0:01:41.000
Zita rangu ndi Roberta uye ini ndinobva ku Spain.

0:01:41.000,0:01:48.760
Chokutanga pane zvose, ndinoda, muzita rine simba ra Jesu Kristu, kuti nditaure zvose, kuti ndifumure dhiyabhorosi

0:01:48.760,0:01:51.060
uye nditaure uchapupu hwangu nhasi.

0:01:51.060,0:01:55.340
Ameni! Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:01:55.340,0:01:59.100
Zviro kwazvo, uchapupu uhwu ndehwekunyadzisa dhiabhorosi pane zvaakaita

0:01:59.100,0:02:01.820
uye kupa mbiri kuna Jesu nokuda kwenunuro Yake muhupenyu hwako.

0:02:01.820,0:02:07.340
Goverana nesu nderipi shoko reuporofita iro wakagamuchira Svondo yapera.

0:02:07.340,0:02:13.280
T.B. Joshua akaprofita kuti ndaiva ne mweya we kukwezva varume uye unobva kumhuri yangu

0:02:13.280,0:02:20.860
uye mweya wakandiisa muupfambi, asi Jesu anondida uye Akanditora akandibuditsa mazviri - Akandiponesa.

0:02:20.860,0:02:22.600
Ndinokutendai, Jesu.

0:02:22.600,0:02:29.280
Hareruya! Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu!

0:02:29.280,0:02:34.680
Goverana nesu zvakaitika muupenyu hwako; unogona sei kusimbisa uporofita uhwu kuva hwechokwadi?

0:02:34.680,0:02:37.720
Mhuri yangu yaiva dambudziko.

0:02:37.720,0:02:40.020
Munhu wese ...

0:02:40.020,0:02:46.720
Handina kumboziva zvazvinoreva kuva nemhuri nokuti munhu wese akarambana;

0:02:46.720,0:02:50.300
vanamainini, amai vangu nababa ...

0:02:50.300,0:02:54.060
Raiva dambudziko - ndakanga ndichitambura zvakanyanya.

0:02:54.060,0:02:55.060
Ndakanga ndichinyengetera, "Ishe ..."

0:02:55.060,0:03:02.340
Ndinorangarira - pandakanga ndiri muduku, ndakanga ndisiri mu Kristu asi ndakangoti, "Ini - handisi kuzorarama saizvozvo".

0:03:02.340,0:03:06.100
Ndakanga ndichinyengetera, "Mwari, ndisunungurei".

0:03:06.100,0:03:16.360
Pandakanga ndava nemakore gumi nemasere, mai vangu vaiwanzoti, "O, vakadzi vari mumhuri yedu vanoda zvapabonde kwazvo ... Usanetseka -

0:03:16.360,0:03:21.900
zvakanaka. Enda unokwezva varume. Hapana chakaipa "

0:03:21.900,0:03:28.740
Ndaigara ndiine muedzo uyu wokutaura nevakomana ne kuwana zvinhu zvandaida.

0:03:28.740,0:03:31.400
Ndakange ndisingambozvinzwisisa kuti sei ...

0:03:31.400,0:03:35.600
Pandaiva ndichiri muduku zvikuru, varume vaigara vachinditarisa zvinoshamisa.

0:03:35.600,0:03:38.220
Handina kumbobvira ndanzwisisa kuti chii chakanga chakaipa pandiri.

0:03:38.220,0:03:45.840
Kunyangwe pandakanga ndakapfeka zvakadzikama, ndisina kuzora mekiapu, pasina chandinacho, ndaiwanzo tariswa zvakanyanya.

0:03:45.840,0:03:49.120
