0:03:49.120,0:03:54.620
Ndakanga ndisina Mweya wa Mwari, panguva iyoyo.

0:03:54.620,0:04:01.640
Ndinoyeuka, pandakanga ndava nemakore gumi nemasere, pandakanga ndichidzokera kumba ndichibva kujimu,

0:04:01.640,0:04:07.500
kwaiva nemurume ainditevera uye pandakapinda mumba mangu

0:04:07.500,0:04:11.700
Akandibvuta ndokundibata panhengo yemuviri wangu yakavanzika.

0:04:11.700,0:04:14.860
Aida kundibudisa kunze kwemba.

0:04:14.860,0:04:21.060
Asi akanga asingazivi kuti ndaigara munzvimbo iyoyo uye amai vangu vakazarura musuo, ndokumuona -

0:04:21.060,0:04:24.480
ipapo akandidonhedzera pasi achibva atiza.

0:04:24.480,0:04:30.540
Saka, Mwari aindiponesa ini nguva dzose kubva kumamiriro ezvinhu ose

0:04:30.540,0:04:35.700
Pandakanga ndiri muhukama hwakadzama, handina kunzwisisa kuti nei ndaitarisa varume,

0:04:35.700,0:04:42.880
nei ndaive nemanzwiro aya okuda varume, nei ndaida ...

0:04:42.880,0:04:44.400
Ndakanga ndisinganzwisise.

0:04:44.400,0:04:47.220
Mwoyo wangu waisada izvozvo asi muviri wangu, nyama yangu ...

0:04:47.220,0:04:52.760
Ndakanga ndichitya kutarisa mukomana, nokuti pandaimutarisa, aibva aiita se ari kupenga.

0:04:52.760,0:05:03.460
Apo ndaienda kujimu, handitombodi kutarisa ani zvake nokuti ndinonzwa sekuti varume vakamirira kuti nditarisane navo.

0:05:03.460,0:05:13.300
Kubva panguva yandakagamuchira Jesu Kristu gore rapfuura, kurwisana kwemweya kwakatanga nokuti ndakatanga kunzwa zvakashata pamusoro pazvo.

0:05:13.300,0:05:22.260
Ndaiziva kuti ndakanga ndisiri kuenda pabonde navo asi ndainzwa ndine mhosva uye ndichisemburwa mukati mangu.

0:05:22.260,0:05:31.860
Ndakanga ndichibvunza Ishe, "Chii chiri kuitika? Sei ndichinzwa kurwa kwemweya uku mandiri?"

0:05:31.860,0:05:36.480
Zvaiva mumusoro wangu ...zvaiva zvechokwadi ...

0:05:36.480,0:05:44.720
Mupfungwa dzangu ndaiziva kuti dai ndisiri mu Kristu, ndingadai ndichifamba-famba nevarume vose ndichinakidzwa,

0:05:44.720,0:05:45.980
Ini ndaisazokwanisa kupedza izvozvo.

0:05:45.980,0:05:47.780
Ndizvo zvakanga zviri mumusoro mangu.

0:05:47.780,0:05:48.900
Izvozvo zvakandityisa chaizvo.

0:05:48.900,0:05:51.940
Ndinoyeuka imwe nguva ndakadzoka kumba nokuti ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kuva muchechi ...

0:05:51.940,0:05:55.180
Ndakafunga, "Ini ndiri mu Kristu, asi ndinonzwa ndakasviba uye ndakaipa".

0:05:55.180,0:06:02.340
Ndakadzokera kumba ndakanga ndichinyengetera kuna Ishe - ndichiti, "Torai mweya wangu ndidzokere kudenga mungopedza nezvangu,

0:06:02.340,0:06:06.700
kana kuti ndidzikinurei, nokuti handidi kurarama saizvozvo. "

0:06:06.700,0:06:10.800
Saka, tiri kunyatsonzwisisa kuti mweya uyu wekukwezva, wembwa,

0:06:10.800,0:06:14.380
wakanyatsokusundira kwose kwose ukaita kuti hupenyu hwako huundundike.

0:06:14.380,0:06:18.480
Iwe wambotaura kare kuti pawakaenda kujimu zvaiita sekuti

0:06:18.480,0:06:21.980
varume vaive vakamirira kuti vatarisane ne maziso ako.

0:06:21.980,0:06:22.960
Iwe ungatii?

0:06:22.960,0:06:27.280
Iwe unofunga kuti waive nesimba mumaziso ako here?

0:06:27.280,0:06:28.240
Ehe.

0:06:28.240,0:06:32.100
Ndichakuudza chinhu chimwe - kwamuri vasikana, teererai kwandiri.

0:06:32.100,0:06:37.900
Ndakanga ndiri mu Kristu uye ndakanga ndichida Mwari - ichi ndicho chikonzero ini ndiri pano ndakasunungurwa ikozvino.

0:06:37.900,0:06:46.240
Mwedzi wakapfuura, pandakaenda kujimu, varume vakanaka vaiti kwandiri, "Wakanaka kwazvo, wakanakisa".

0:06:46.240,0:06:50.840
Unogona kufunga kuti pamwe angave mu Kristu mune ramangwana, murume wako kana chii.

0:06:50.840,0:06:56.160
Ndaimboti, "Ini ndiri mu Kristu, ini handigoni kusangana newe."

0:06:56.160,0:07:01.380
Apo pavanotanga kutaura newe iwe wobva waratidza kuve une chivimbo chikuru, vangati,

0:07:01.380,0:07:06.840
"O, ndinoda kuverenga Bhaibheri newe, ndinoda kuziva nezva Mwari, zvimwe unganditungamirira kuna Mwari?"

0:07:06.840,0:07:11.120
Izvozvo inhema!

0:07:11.120,0:07:15.660
Kunyangwe ndisati ndauya ku SCOAN, kwaiva nemurume ...

0:07:15.660,0:07:17.460
Ndinotenda Mwari kuti handina kurara naye.

0:07:17.460,0:07:19.440
Munoziva zvaakandiudza pandakanga ndichienda kumba?

0:07:19.440,0:07:25.300
Akati, "Kubvira ikozvino, iwe uchafunga nezvangu, uye iwe uchandikumbira kuti ndikufonere,

0:07:25.300,0:07:28.220
uye uchida zvepabonde neni, nekupedzisa zvatatanga. "

0:07:28.220,0:07:29.720
Iro idhimoni.

0:07:29.720,0:07:36.200
Uyu haasi mukomana anoda kuziva Bhaibheri, uyo haasi mu Kristu uye haasi kubva kuna Mwari!

0:07:36.200,0:07:38.440
Wawu, isu tinogona kunyatsonzwisisa kuti mweya iyi ...

0:07:38.440,0:07:41.460
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu

0:07:41.460,0:07:45.760
nekununura hanzvadzi yedu kubva kune izvo zvingadai zvakave hupenyu hunotyisa kwazvo chaizvoizvo.

0:07:45.760,0:07:50.700
Tiudzei, ndezvipi zvimwe zvezvinhu, izvo mweya uyu wekukwezva wakakukurudzira iwe kuti uite,

0:07:50.700,0:07:55.900
zvawave zvino, ne kununurwa kwawaita wave kuzvidemba

0:07:55.900,0:07:58.620
Munoziva, ndinozvidemba ...

0:07:58.620,0:07:59.300
Ndingazvitaura sei?

0:07:59.300,0:08:01.420
Mweya uyu ...

0:08:01.420,0:08:05.420
Dai ndakanga ndafa, ndingadai ndakaenda kugehena.

0:08:05.420,0:08:10.060
Ndizvo zvandinozvidemba zvikuru - kuti ini ...

0:08:10.060,0:08:10.840
Ndoreva...

0:08:10.840,0:08:19.580
Ndicho chaiva chinhu: Mwari akaponesa mwoyo wangu, Akaponesa mweya wangu nokuti dai ndakanga ndafa, ndingadai ndakaenda kugehena

0:08:19.580,0:08:23.520
Mwari mutsvene uye anovenga chivi.

0:08:23.520,0:08:31.500
Ndizvo zvandinozvidemba: kuita chivi, kusa dzikinurwa ne kusarwisa dhiyabhori zvakanyanya -

0:08:31.500,0:08:34.120
asi zvakaoma kana iwe usati waponeswa.

0:08:34.120,0:08:35.520
Zvakanaka. Tinonzwisisa.

0:08:35.520,0:08:39.520
Zvino, kukubwinya kwa Mwari - iwe wati waida kunyadzisa dhiyabhorosi

0:08:39.520,0:08:42.260
