0:08:48.160,0:08:54.060
Ndezvipi zvinhu zvaunoda kureurura ikozvino, pamberi pa Mwari?

0:08:54.060,0:08:57.600
Nyadzi, kusembura ...

0:08:57.600,0:09:00.800
Ndakanga ndichirota ndiri pabonde nevarume.

0:09:00.800,0:09:07.520
Ndakarotawo hope apo murume wacho aiti kwandiri, "Iwe hapana chauchabura. Hausi chinhu.

0:09:07.520,0:09:13.380
Iwe unosemesa. Ini ndichakutora. Iwe haugoni kuwana zvaunoda. "

0:09:13.380,0:09:16.540
Vaigara vachitaura neni kuburikidza nevanhu, kunyange va Kristu.

0:09:16.540,0:09:23.580
Mungafungidzira izvo vakandiudza, "Iwe uchagara wakadaro zvachose. Hauzochinja"?

0:09:23.580,0:09:27.000
Ndiyo nzira iyo dhiyabhorosi aive achindikonzeresa kuti ndiite.

0:09:27.000,0:09:28.960
Icho chaiva chiitiko chakaipisisa kwandiri.

0:09:28.960,0:09:34.000
Uyezve, ndaifunga kuti handizomboroorwa nokuti ndaisagona kugadzikana.

0:09:34.000,0:09:39.260
Ndaive nemunhu wandaidana naye asi ndaifunga nezvekuita chimwe chinhu nevamwe varume.

