0:10:16.840,0:10:20.020
Ndaive ndichimupomera mhosva.

0:10:20.020,0:10:25.280
Ndaimubvunza, " Haunzwi saizvozvo here? Usanyepa. Ini ndinonzwa saizvozvo."

0:10:25.280,0:10:26.380
Handaikwanisa kunzwisisa.

0:10:26.380,0:10:30.300
Ndakanga ndichifunga kuti munhu wose aive nemanzwiro akadaro.

0:10:30.300,0:10:36.100
Apo ini ndakataura naamai vangu ndichiti, "Handizivi kuti chii chiri kuitika kwandiri.Ndiri kunzwa ndichida zvekudanana nevarume,

0:10:36.100,0:10:39.380
