Zvakakuita kuti unzwe sei iwe pachako, uchiziva kuti iwe wairamba uine maziso kune murume wose ari mukamuri iyoyo?

0:11:10.680,0:11:13.540
Pandakanga ndisiri mu Kristu, izvo zvaiita kuti ndinzwe zvakanaka.

