Apo ndakatanga kuverenga Shoko ra Mwari, apo Jesu akabata mwoyo wangu, ndakanzwa zvakashata.

0:11:28.180,0:11:31.300
Ndakatofunga kuti Mwari haandide.

0:11:31.300,0:11:35.300
Pari zvino, mushure mekudzikinurwa, nguva dzose apo ...

